data.eml:eml: Nine new species of Megaselia Rondani (Diptera: Phoridae) from the Seychelles

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Disney, R. Henry L. (2006): Nine new species of Megaselia Rondani (Diptera: Phoridae) from the Seychelles. Zootaxa 1210: 1-25, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.172462
